Silver Line Train Schedule

Technologies used: Firebase, HTML, CSS, Moments and jQuery

In this app you can:

  • Check SilverLine train schedule.
  • Add Train line and schedule. Please enter train frequency in minutes only.
  • You can update (name, trtainnumber, frequency) and even delete the train schedule.
  • Trains arriving in 4 mins or less will highlight in the schedule.
